---
title: Spaghetti and Turkey Meatballs with Rustic Tomato Sauce and Baby Spinach
description: We're serving up this classic dish with a few special touches. The meatballs are made with turkey and we've secretly packed the satisfying tomato sauce with veggies for a wholesome take on a crowd-pleasing comfort food.
